1
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:35,660
Winter Begonia

2
00:01:35,660 --> 00:01:38,020
Episode 5

3
00:01:47,220 --> 00:01:48,500
Are you still in bed?

4
00:01:51,250 --> 00:01:52,200
Come on. Get up.

5
00:01:52,229 --> 00:01:53,539
I know you’re awake.

6
00:01:55,020 --> 00:01:57,380
Where did you and Xirui go yesterday?

7
00:01:58,180 --> 00:01:59,410
Did you hurt him?

8
00:02:01,160 --> 00:02:02,690
I didn’t.

9
00:02:04,460 --> 00:02:07,520
We just took a walk around the town.

10
00:02:08,370 --> 00:02:10,449
You can ask Mr. Ge.

11
00:02:11,900 --> 00:02:13,160
Don’t even mention him.

12
00:02:13,580 --> 00:02:14,760
Look what you did to that poor man.

13
00:02:18,790 --> 00:02:19,770
What happened to him?

14
00:02:20,390 --> 00:02:21,900
He got a fever after he went home.

15
00:02:23,050 --> 00:02:24,010
Well…

16
00:02:24,170 --> 00:02:26,070
Get a doctor to see him now.

17
00:02:26,610 --> 00:02:28,030
Before it gets worse.

18
00:02:28,060 --> 00:02:29,390
I already did.

19
00:02:30,590 --> 00:02:32,260
Now drink up this ginger soup.

20
00:02:33,490 --> 00:02:35,820
I can’t. I’m too sleepy.

21
00:02:36,110 --> 00:02:37,180
What are you talking about?

22
00:02:37,420 --> 00:02:39,210
What if you get sick?

23
00:02:39,460 --> 00:02:41,020
Can’t have you pass it to the kid.

24
00:02:45,720 --> 00:02:46,640
Get up now.

25
00:02:47,510 --> 00:02:49,140
Get out of the bed.

26
00:02:49,670 --> 00:02:50,290
Hurry up.

27
00:02:52,100 --> 00:02:52,710
Come on.

28
00:02:57,430 --> 00:02:59,760
All you care about these days are the kid.

29
00:03:00,390 --> 00:03:02,340
Shouldn’t have had him at the first place.

30
00:03:03,510 --> 00:03:05,010
Look at you being all silly.

31
00:03:05,500 --> 00:03:07,390
Jealous of your own son?

32
00:03:09,090 --> 00:03:10,180
I just

33
00:03:13,110 --> 00:03:15,180
can’t have my wife

34
00:03:15,210 --> 00:03:16,970
thinking about someone else.

35
00:03:17,550 --> 00:03:19,250
Not even my own son.

36
00:03:21,150 --> 00:03:22,470
There there.

37
00:03:22,610 --> 00:03:23,380
You’re a big boy now.

38
00:03:23,410 --> 00:03:24,770
Don’t be a baby.

39
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,120
Childe Cao

40
00:03:28,150 --> 00:03:29,850
sent an adjutant over

41
00:03:30,530 --> 00:03:31,850
with a lot of presents.

42
00:03:32,450 --> 00:03:33,740
Saying that the commander

43
00:03:33,770 --> 00:03:34,970
fired a shot yesterday.

44
00:03:35,390 --> 00:03:36,850
And he had to make sure

45
00:03:36,880 --> 00:03:37,810
that we’re all okay.

46
00:03:39,870 --> 00:03:40,850
Cao Guixiu?

47
00:03:43,920 --> 00:03:45,530
Just tell them that I’m ill and can’t see them.

48
00:03:46,020 --> 00:03:47,450
They’re family.

49
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:48,890
Why would you lie to them?

50
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,730
You don’t know.

51
00:03:51,930 --> 00:03:53,400
My nephew

52
00:03:53,430 --> 00:03:55,079
is very ambitious.

53
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:57,920
He wants to get rid of that commander father of his

54
00:03:57,950 --> 00:03:59,120
and be the new king.

55
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:02,210
I can’t be too close to him.

56
00:04:03,270 --> 00:04:06,380
That’ll make me a traitor.

57
00:04:08,710 --> 00:04:10,010
You’re not wrong.

58
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,710
Even if they got back together afterwards,

59
00:04:12,740 --> 00:04:14,200
you can’t help either of them.

60
00:04:15,070 --> 00:04:16,470
I’m just worried that we’ll upset him.

61
00:04:16,500 --> 00:04:18,480
You sister has some hard choice to make.

62
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,480
If she doesn’t make the hard decision now,

63
00:04:21,649 --> 00:04:23,660
things will be even harder for her after this.

64
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:26,170
Just tell her that.

65
00:04:31,940 --> 00:04:35,360
(Peking Times)

66
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:37,020
Shang Xirui upset Commander Cao.
(Peking Times)

67
00:04:37,020 --> 00:04:37,610
Shang Xirui upset Commander Cao.

68
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:40,110
Tension Heightens.

69
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:44,940
Let me see.

70
00:04:51,270 --> 00:04:52,070
This is bad.

71
00:04:52,409 --> 00:04:53,830
I almost forgot about this.

72
00:04:55,060 --> 00:04:56,090
Where are you going?

73
00:04:56,330 --> 00:04:57,490
I have to head out.

74
00:04:59,140 --> 00:04:59,850
What’s wrong?

75
00:05:03,300 --> 00:05:04,530
You’re having a fever!

76
00:05:05,060 --> 00:05:06,500
What happened yesterday

77
00:05:06,530 --> 00:05:08,950
was truly frightening.

78
00:05:09,480 --> 00:05:11,210
Thank god that Shang Xirui

79
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:13,410
can only sing and talk.

80
00:05:13,580 --> 00:05:14,880
If he had done anything physical

81
00:05:14,910 --> 00:05:16,810
the commander could’ve shot him right there.

82
00:05:17,010 --> 00:05:17,610
I don’t think so.

83
00:05:19,550 --> 00:05:20,450
Shang Xirui

84
00:05:20,780 --> 00:05:22,290
has some gut.

85
00:05:22,780 --> 00:05:24,170
Our commander values him.

86
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,010
Otherwise, he would’ve shot him

87
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:25,840
back in Pingyang.

88
00:05:27,310 --> 00:05:28,690
I’m sorry, Adjutant Sun.

89
00:05:30,130 --> 00:05:32,220
Mr. Cheng personally went to talk to Shang Xirui last night,

90
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:34,460
after he found out what he’d done.

91
00:05:34,490 --> 00:05:35,990
He got sick after that.

92
00:05:36,470 --> 00:05:38,980
He’s now still in bed with a fever.

93
00:05:39,710 --> 00:05:40,659
He’s not well.

94
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:42,810
Should we get a doctor over?

95
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:44,420
Can’t let him get the pneumonia.

96
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:46,610
I know a doctor from the west

97
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:48,880
who specializes in these illnesses.

98
00:05:49,140 --> 00:05:50,200
Should we get him

99
00:05:50,230 --> 00:05:51,340
to check on Mr. Cheng?

100
00:05:51,810 --> 00:05:52,950
Don’t bother.

101
00:05:53,170 --> 00:05:55,550
He’ll be better after a bowl of ginger soup.

102
00:05:55,830 --> 00:05:56,610
He just can’t make it here today

103
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:58,290
