104
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:00,110
Don’t be a stranger.

105
00:06:00,700 --> 00:06:02,430
I am simply here

106
00:06:02,460 --> 00:06:03,600
to see Mr. Cheng.

107
00:06:05,140 --> 00:06:07,090
The presents are delivered.

108
00:06:07,530 --> 00:06:09,830
Our job is done here.

109
00:06:10,380 --> 00:06:11,260
Please thank the Childe

110
00:06:11,290 --> 00:06:12,690
for both of us.

111
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,250
Sure. Thank you.

112
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:15,330
See you.

113
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:25,850
What are these journalists talking about?

114
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:27,320
What is this nonsense?

115
00:06:27,680 --> 00:06:28,370
Our leader can’t perform

116
