146
00:07:42,760 --> 00:07:44,680
The rent of half a year all at once…

147
00:07:45,170 --> 00:07:45,890
Even with someone as popular as

148
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,159
our leader,

149
00:07:47,190 --> 00:07:48,950
